{"tid":13681,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]懷疑自己有精神病,需唔需要睇精神科","createTime":"2016-11-30T07:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-14T10:15:08.000Z","uid":11046,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"953bd58819abf69a023e7106576c865ea438c9c8","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"有以下徵狀,懷疑自己有精神病,想請求意見咁樣有冇需要睇心理/精神科醫生。<br />\n1.無法與同齡同事/同學溝通<br />\n2.返學無法寫出抒情文,但議論文/數理OK<br />\n3.聽唔明人地講野,尤其是婉轉語法,只明白表面意思<br />\nEX.人地鬧我去死,我會立即諗點唔犯法地令對方消失,唔識原諒人地係因為火遮眼<br />\n4.與人對話時,無法組織完整句子,同講野太直<br />\nEX.人地做大耳窿,我當住人面話佢會有報應(知咁   講唔岩但無法控制)<br />\n5.壓制自己暴力傾向=說服自己該人有利用價值/         殺人犯法,而非因為對方是親人/朋友<br />\n6.無法控制地摵皮+著一隻拖鞋<br />\n7.唔會同人主動交談<br />\n真係好辛苦,經常因為講野太直,比人覺得我冇禮貌,所以更加唔想同人溝通,仲曾經比家人鬧過自閉"},{"pid":"7c978f2a80b383291a94ac7c1bc69356e8e9d185","tid":13681,"uid":16016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打好危險"},{"pid":"2eebae1e6df904806cca7c2c603f096869eedb5d","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:35:51.000Z","msg":"其實我都知自己危險,亦問過2個做醫護既同學,但佢地覺得知自己痴線就唔算痴線囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa30300cfda88ea5dfd70978376e1258e4b8d9eb","tid":13681,"uid":16016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:37:33.000Z","msg":"有冇惡化傾向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70fa288be539d9bdf01871b572e710449384d73","tid":13681,"uid":37272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"我地呢啲叫天才，咁先夠特別架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗理會世俗嘅眼光！活在當下"},{"pid":"07e441871ab217b4c79fbf31251e024d01204679","tid":13681,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"似自閉加抑鬱"},{"pid":"e98d180b26011ca3fee4c838d5d96396a595a6a9","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇惡化傾向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇乜,不過讀書期間就努力扮正常,其實EQ咁多年都冇進步過,比人話唔識大"},{"pid":"70c4458bf69a9cf7438b6d967accfbceb798fd70","tid":13681,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:39:26.000Z","msg":"係咪賤種皇?"},{"pid":"3693c4d18af95c5466cc48d96ce3743e04b56add","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地呢啲叫天才，咁先夠特別架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗理會世俗嘅眼光！活在當下</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀..因為比伴侶話奇怪,有D介意:("},{"pid":"c335fb2af4dd8663621b841e2a35d135c9e5aebe","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似自閉加抑鬱</blockquote><br />\n但我尚算溝通到,只係技巧極差,咁係自閉咩"},{"pid":"d3a99b0c02709920ca8046b9329f8bead614b35d","tid":13681,"uid":37272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:43:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我地呢啲叫天才，咁先夠特別架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗理會世俗嘅眼光！活在當下</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀..因為比伴侶話奇怪,有D介意:(</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係得有左手同右手陪我傾計，你有伴侶已經好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d417825c2501b15ab74ef74c5ebd1727fea964","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;我地呢啲叫天才，咁先夠特別架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗理會世俗嘅眼光！活在當下&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n唔係呀..因為比伴侶話奇怪,有D介意:(&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n我都係得有左手同右手陪我傾計，你有伴侶已經好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍拖都係扮下正常,但係結左婚好難扮落去,就比佢話奇怪,你睇我好我睇你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d2eb27b774240c9b94413a275c96f5d31e2269","tid":13681,"uid":37272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;我地呢啲叫天才，咁先夠特別架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗理會世俗嘅眼光！活在當下&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n唔係呀..因為比伴侶話奇怪,有D介意:(&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n我都係得有左手同右手陪我傾計，你有伴侶已經好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍拖都係扮下正常,但係結左婚好難扮落去,就比佢話奇怪,你睇我好我睇你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明嘅！為左融入正常嘅社會，都要扮下正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我試過做運動去抒發情緒都幾有效！你都可以試下，咩都唔諗自己跑下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3132c72ff43e51a1de0dd4f7bb18aa2769705e","tid":13681,"uid":37272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"再逼自己更會令世人看不透而去中傷自己"},{"pid":"c0674ff536399392a4ad71e2ec10b10fbce6d64e","tid":13681,"uid":9664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"巴打可以去有啲有社區精神科文憑嘅家庭醫生睇吓先<br />\n如果巴打你唔太嚴重的話佢哋都會開到藥畀你食<br />\n但如果去睇精神科就千鳩幾一鑊<br />\n冇病都睇到病"},{"pid":"459d4d70e3ac203628c07f637d0f5ff0de4abbaf","tid":13681,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都知自己危險,亦問過2個做醫護既同學,但佢地覺得知自己痴線就唔算痴線囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地on9 <br />\n睇下醫生啦"},{"pid":"58a2d5a7b7cb210d5731d0d95a97c8e252216f7c","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再逼自己更會令世人看不透而去中傷自己</blockquote><br />\n我而家可以打機,搣皮,同講粗口控制其他暴力傾向,但係佢呢3樣都唔鐘意囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哈哈哈哈哈嘻嘻嘻"},{"pid":"02b2837b5f647c26c64360aa474ec37a2399e604","tid":13681,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"2.返學無法寫出抒情文,但議論文/數理OK<br />\n<br />\n屌你我都唔識寫抒情文，唔通又有精神病？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc8c5b6d28edde0e79af4a02a6bd56862b93ccd","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"多謝各位意見,我會去睇下自己係咪傻架啦"},{"pid":"033297f45bd78454c573c61844a3bb3bae623a03","tid":13681,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"同埋1 個項<br />\n點樣溝通唔到先<br />\n純粹話題唔岩定一講野就好易鬧交/不歡而散？"},{"pid":"be0ebdf06bc875cc2c9cb16af49a5f5c127aef1a","tid":13681,"uid":9664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝各位意見,我會去睇下自己係咪傻架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情緒病啫....大把人有....<br />\n千祈唔好label自己儍佬...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ded1c2f9945b061e5a6eb21d21a8b2a81b4c27d","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2.返學無法寫出抒情文,但議論文/數理OK<br />\n<br />\n屌你我都唔識寫抒情文，唔通又有精神病？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下..我唔知架,可能你都有呢呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fd3a42faa785aa3324adb1ea4d6c9e316c4430","tid":13681,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"巴打你唔好獻世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95239ac10d6ee0793490f86f9d2559fdf18e8533","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋1 個項<br />\n點樣溝通唔到先<br />\n純粹話題唔岩定一講野就好易鬧交/不歡而散？</blockquote><br />\n就係一講野就好易嘈交,好易嬲,人地笑住講我盲,唔識野,  我會認真咁鬧佢你就真係唔撚識野啦,跟住拎人地痛腳出黎攻擊人"},{"pid":"ae90a99a87e202037d1266ce646c045d3fb0deeb","tid":13681,"uid":11046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你唔好獻世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吹咩呵呵  有排獻世呀我"}]}